node.text:
We work with the world’s best independent testing facilities to reach both ECE and DOT safety standards for all ATLAS helmets. They test every imaginable variable to ensure sure that our helmets exceed the standards that you expect when considering a new helmet. 

The VIAS Institute starts with testing 50 ATLAS helmets, assessing impact points all over the shell to make sure that standards are met and that your helmet keeps you protected when you need it most. They test different angles of impact, shape of object impacting the helmet as well as various impact velocities. 

But this is just the beginning. Atlas helmets are submitted to VIAS for regular batch testing and conformity checks!

ATLAS helmets are shipped all over the world, to every imaginable climate. VIAS test our gear in the extreme conditions that you might face. Whether you’re riding through a blizzard or carving turns in the desert canyons, our helmets have been engineered to meet those safety standards, whatever the weather. 

The revolutionary Fidlock system that ships with every helmet is tested by the VIAS Institute to ensure that the safety standard for buckle retention is met, meaning you can be sure that your buckle will remain secure if under load during an accident. 

Ride with confidence, knowing that your ATLAS 3.0 is tried and tested by the best.

node.text: What's up guys. Matt Rees here. Co-founder of Ruroc. I wanted to put a message out to tell you about an incredible new mission of ours. @Enginehawk. Since we launched Atlas, we've found it hard to find motorcycle clothing that matches the level of design and performance of our helmets. We found that the gear we were forced to use was old school. It lacked great design, fit poorly, and the armor made it downright uncomfortable. And so we built a team. We recruited world class designers, and experts in engineering from the motorcycle industry. The result? motorcycle gear that looks better, fits better, and protects better. On April 27th, Enginehawk launches its first range of INSANE products. Follow the page for our new product releases over the next month and enjoy all the epic sh*t we've got to show you in the run up to the launch! #Ruroc #Enginehawk

To keep up with demand for Ruroc helmets, we’ve ditched the supply chains that big brands use and built our own factory. Every helmet that comes out of our new state of the art facility will be made faster, stronger and better quality than ever before, while ensuring the best working conditions for our staff.

The Ruroc factory is the next step in our mission to become the best helmet brand in the world. 💪
